@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ktnisr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos(0.98))
    v2 = v0
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.82 + v0 + 0.57) + (tmp + 0.85 - tmp + 0.58)) * (0.31 / v1))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.79 / tmp + 0.93)) * wp.abs((v1 + 0.88 * v2 + 0.85)))
    v1 = v0
    tmp = (0.57 + 0.53)
    data[tid] = v0
